---
title: Haloumi & Dukkah Roast Veggie Bowl with Yoghurt Dressing
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Slices of flavourful haloumi meet roasted vegetables tossed with dukkah, and there’s a tangy, refreshing yoghurt dressing and roasted almonds to finish it off. Get ready to eat the world!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/dukkah-roast-veggies-haloumi-4322be32.jpg
